-takes-a-powerful-turn-after-olympic-champion-alysa-lius-heartfelt-tribute-steals-attention%2Farticleshow%2F129845571.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%8B%E2%80%98Harry%20Potter%E2%80%99%20TV%20show%20cast%20guide%3A%20Who%E2%80%99s%20playing%20who%3F%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129845655.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGet%20ready%20to%20head%20back%20to%20Hogwarts.%20HBO's%20new%20'Harry%20Potter'%20series%20lands%20this%20Christmas%202026%2C%20and%20they're%20doing%20things%20differently%3A%20each%20of%20J.K.%20Rowling%E2%80%99s%20seven%20books%20gets%20its%20own%20season.%20So%2C%20%E2%80%98Philosopher%E2%80%99s%20Stone%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Chamber%20of%20Secrets%E2%80%99%2C%20all%20the%20way%20to%20%E2%80%98Deathly%20Hallows%E2%80%99%20are%20back%2C%20but%20in%20a%20bigger%2C%20longer%20format.Dominic%20McLaughlin%20steps%20into%20Harry%E2%80%99s%20shoes.%20You%20probably%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20him%20yet%2C%20as%20he%E2%80%99s%20pretty%20new%20to%20the%20scene.%20Per%20Variety%2C%20he%20played%20in%20Sky%E2%80%99s%20comedy%20%E2%80%98Grow%E2%80%99%20alongside%20his%20soon-to-be%20Hagrid%2C%20Nick%20Frost.%20Arabella%20Stanton%20takes%20on%20Hermione%2C%20and%20she%20was%20Matilda%20on%20the%20West%20End%20stage%2C%20so%20she%E2%80%99s%20got%20that%20classic%20book-smart%20energy.%20Alastair%20Stout%20is%20embodying%20Ron%2C%20and%2C%20honestly%2C%20this%20is%20his%20first%20real%20gig.%20These%20are%20fresh%20faces%2C%20and%20HBO%20went%20big%3A%20there%20were%2032%2C000%20auditioning%20kids%20for%20Harry%E2%80%99s%20role.%20Mark%20Mylod%20and%20his%20casting%20team%20sifted%20through%20hundreds%20of%20tapes%20every%20single%20day.John%20Lithgow%2C%20who%20already%20is%20a%20legend%2C%20plays%20Professor%20Dumbledore.%20Paapa%20Essiedu%20is%20Snape.%20Janet%20McTeer%20is%20Professor%20McGonagall.%20Nick%20Frost%20brings%20Hagrid%20to%20life.%20Bel%20Powley%20and%20Daniel%20Rigby%20are%20Harry's%20awful%20Aunt%20Petunia%20and%20Uncle%20Vernon.Looking%20at%20Season%201%2C%20Paul%20Whitehouse%20takes%20the%20cranky%20caretaker%20Argus%20Filch%2C%20Luke%20Thallon%20is%20Professor%20Quirrell%2C%20Katherine%20Parkinson%20becomes%20Molly%20Weasley%2C%20Lox%20Pratt%20plays%20Draco%20Malfoy%2C%20and%20Johnny%20Flynn%20is%20Lucius%20Malfoy.Francesca%20Gardiner%20heads%20up%20the%20writing%20and%20executive%20producing%3B%20she%E2%80%99s%20running%20the%20show.%20Mark%20Mylod%20is%20directing%20and%20executive%20producing%2C%20teaming%20up%20with%20Bront%C3%AB%20Film%20and%20TV%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Rowling%20herself%20is%20involved%20as%20an%20executive%20producer%2C%20along%20with%20Neil%20Blair%2C%20Ruth%20Kenley-Letts%2C%20and%20David%20Heyman%20from%20Heyday%20Films.Here%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20unpack%20the%20full%20cast%20and%20learn%20about%20who%E2%80%99s%20playing%20who.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774609602000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129845655%2Cimgsize-154002.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fharry-potter-tv-show-cast-guide-whos-playing-who%2Fphotostory%2F129845655.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Lightning%20Hits%20Burj%20Khalifa%3A%20Here's%20How%20Building%20Protects%20Itself%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22The%20towering%20skyscraper%2C%20measuring%202%2C272%20feet%2C%20was%20hit%20as%20dark%20clouds%2C%20rain%20and%20thunder%20rolled%20across%20Dubai's%20skyline.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774609451000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-03%2F06v275hs_burj-khalifa-_625x300_27_March_26.jpeg%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmassive-lightning-hits-burj-khalifa-heres-how-building-protects-itself-11273917%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Candace%20Owens%20accuses%20Erika%20Kirk%20of%20plotting%20Charlie%20Kir